his is something more, something akin to \u003cem\u003eValheim \u003c/em\u003eor \u003cem\u003eEnshrouded\u003c/em\u003e. But even if you have experience in survival/crafting games, this one does things a little differently. After spending an hour with the game, there are a few things you should know before diving into \u003cem\u003eRuneScape Dragonwilds\u003c/em\u003e! - Brandon Morgan \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/runescape-dragonwilds-first-base-woodcutting-cows-camp-1851780655\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/runescape-dragonwilds-first-base-woodcutting-cows-camp-1851780655\"\u003eRead More\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure id=\"\" data-id=\"6799d061c12455322c98e1f726b4d388\" data-recommend-id=\"image://6799d061c12455322c98e1f726b4d388\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"An exterior view of the Chorrol player house in Oblivion Remastered.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt=\"An exterior view of the Chorrol player house in Oblivion Remastered.\" data-link-reference=\"\" data-link-target=\"\" data-syndicationrights=\"true\" data-imagerights=\"fair-use\" data-hide=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 49.94em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_965/6799d061c12455322c98e1f726b4d388.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 50em) and (max-width: 63.69em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1315/6799d061c12455322c98e1f726b4d388.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 63.75em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1600/6799d061c12455322c98e1f726b4d388.jpg\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"An exterior view of the Chorrol player house in Oblivion Remastered.\" data-chomp-id=\"6799d061c12455322c98e1f726b4d388\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-height=\"1080\" data-alt=\"An exterior view of the Chorrol player house in Oblivion Remastered.\" data-anim-src=\"\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/6799d061c12455322c98e1f726b4d388.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eScreenshot: Bethesda / Brandon Morgan / Kotaku\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cspan data-id=\"6799d061c12455322c98e1f726b4d388\" data-recommend-id=\"image://6799d061c12455322c98e1f726b4d388\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"An exterior view of the Chorrol player house in Oblivion Remastered.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eAs you explore the lands of Cyrodiil, you’ll find that waiting in the entrance of a cave or renting a room at the local inn doesn’t suffice for very long. You desire more, a place to call your own, a spot to put down roots in this fantasy land. You need a house in \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/games/the-elder-scrolls-iv-oblivion\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/games/the-elder-scrolls-iv-oblivion\"\u003e\u003cem\u003eOblivion Remastered\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e for numerous reasons, and it’s not to entice an Argonian over for a wine and dine evening. Hey, I don’t judge! But a house comes with amenities such as a free bed, a non-respawning container, and upgrades that allow you to keep up with ever-leveling foes. - Brandon Morgan \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/oblivion-remastered-buy-home-free-house-gold-1851780889\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/oblivion-remastered-buy-home-free-house-gold-1851780889\"\u003eRead More\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure id=\"\" data-id=\"25e137ef35f8727a475076b5d23de434\" data-recommend-id=\"image://25e137ef35f8727a475076b5d23de434\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1696\" data-height=\"954\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"An NPC hides behind a mask.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt=\"An NPC hides behind a mask.\" data-link-reference=\"\" data-link-target=\"\" data-syndicationrights=\"true\" data-imagerights=\"fair-use\" data-hide=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 49.94em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_965/25e137ef35f8727a475076b5d23de434.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 50em) and (max-width: 63.69em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1315/25e137ef35f8727a475076b5d23de434.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 63.75em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1600/25e137ef35f8727a475076b5d23de434.jpg\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"An NPC hides behind a mask.\" data-chomp-id=\"25e137ef35f8727a475076b5d23de434\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-height=\"954\" data-alt=\"An NPC hides behind a mask.\" data-anim-src=\"\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/25e137ef35f8727a475076b5d23de434.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eScreenshot: Ubisoft / Kotaku\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cspan data-id=\"25e137ef35f8727a475076b5d23de434\" data-reco